stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_check_data: validate blob transaction fields
    q_check_data --> q_error_no_data: blob_versioned_hashes is empty
    q_check_data --> q_check_count: blob_versioned_hashes is non-empty
    q_error_no_data --> [*]: raise NoBlobDataError
    q_check_count --> q_error_count: len(blob_versioned_hashes) exceeds MAX_BLOB_COUNT
    q_check_count --> q_check_gas: len(blob_versioned_hashes) <= MAX_BLOB_COUNT
    q_error_count --> [*]: raise BlobCountExceededError
    q_check_gas --> q_error_gas: total_blob_gas exceeds limit
    q_check_gas --> q_check_fee: total_blob_gas within limit
    q_error_gas --> [*]: raise BlobGasLimitExceededError
    q_check_fee --> q_error_fee: max_fee_per_blob_gas less than blob_base_fee
    q_check_fee --> q_check_hash: max_fee_per_blob_gas >= blob_base_fee
    q_error_fee --> [*]: raise InsufficientMaxFeePerBlobGasError
    q_check_hash --> q_iter: for hash in blob_versioned_hashes
    q_iter --> q_error_hash: hash version != VERSIONED_HASH_VERSION_KZG
    q_iter --> q_next: hash version == VERSIONED_HASH_VERSION_KZG
    q_error_hash --> [*]: raise InvalidBlobVersionedHashError
    q_next --> q_iter: more hashes remaining
    q_next --> [*]: all hashes validated
